# CODEOWNERS - Guardian approval requirements for personhood-critical surfaces
# 
# This file defines which paths require multi-party guardian approval before merge.
# See docs/AGI_CHARTER.md and docs/security/SECURITY_GOVERNANCE.md for details.
#
# Guardian Groups:
# - @org/security-guardians (Primary Guardian - Security Lead)
# - @org/memory-guardians (Memory Guardian - Data Lead)
# - @org/ethics-guardians (Ethics Guardian - Ethics Committee)
#
# Approval Requirements:
# - Routine personhood changes: 2 of 3 guardians
# - Core values/ethics changes: All 3 guardians
# - Emergency overrides: Documented in security-waivers.yml

# =============================================================================
# PERSONHOOD-CRITICAL SURFACES (HIGHEST PROTECTION)
# =============================================================================

# AGI Charter and Ethics Framework (requires all 3 guardians)
/docs/AGI_CHARTER.md                          @org/security-guardians @org/memory-guardians @org/ethics-guardians
/docs/AGI_IDENTITY_SPECIFICATION.md           @org/security-guardians @org/memory-guardians @org/ethics-guardians
/docs/AGI_CHARTER_v1_original.md              @org/security-guardians @org/memory-guardians @org/ethics-guardians

# Core AI Systems - FourLaws, Persona, Memory (requires all 3 guardians)
/src/app/core/ai_systems.py                   @org/security-guardians @org/memory-guardians @org/ethics-guardians

# Ethics Configuration (requires all 3 guardians)
/config/ethics_constraints.yml                @org/security-guardians @org/ethics-guardians

# Identity System Modules (requires 2 of 3 guardians)
/src/app/core/identity_*.py                   @org/security-guardians @org/memory-guardians
/src/app/core/meta_identity*.py               @org/security-guardians @org/memory-guardians

# Governance Modules (requires all 3 guardians)
/src/app/core/governance*.py                  @org/security-guardians @org/memory-guardians @org/ethics-guardians

# Memory and Persistence (requires 2 of 3 guardians)
/data/ai_persona/**                           @org/security-guardians @org/memory-guardians
/data/memory/**                               @org/memory-guardians @org/ethics-guardians
/data/identities/**                           @org/security-guardians @org/memory-guardians
/src/app/core/memory*.py                      @org/memory-guardians @org/ethics-guardians

# Learning Request System - Black Vault (requires 2 of 3 guardians)
/src/app/core/learning_paths.py               @org/memory-guardians @org/ethics-guardians
/data/learning_requests/**                    @org/memory-guardians @org/ethics-guardians

# =============================================================================
# SECURITY & GOVERNANCE DOCUMENTATION (SECURITY + ETHICS)
# =============================================================================

/docs/SECURITY_FRAMEWORK.md                   @org/security-guardians @org/ethics-guardians
/docs/security/SECURITY_GOVERNANCE.md         @org/security-guardians @org/ethics-guardians
/docs/security/THREAT_MODEL_SECURITY_WORKFLOWS.md @org/security-guardians @org/ethics-guardians

